===1.11.0 (2021-04-01)===
*Feature: Allow setting a custom terrain type to define highest peak ({{en/GHIssue|8891}})
*Feature: Auto-detect map height limit based on generated map 
*Feature: Setting to indicate desert coverage for tropic climate and snow coverage for arctic climate (replaces snow line height) ({{en/GHIssue|8891}})
*Add: Allow setting the highest mountain for heightmaps ({{en/GHIssue|8891}})
*Change: Scale exported heightmaps to highest peak and inform the user of this value ({{en/GHIssue|8891}})
*Change: Remove "maximum map height" from the New Game GUI ({{en/GHIssue|8891}})
*Fix ({{en/GHIssue|8803}}): Only auto-remove signals when rail can be built ({{en/GHIssue|8904}})
*Fix ({{en/GHIssue|8565}}): Stopped road vehicle displays a speed different than 0 ({{en/GHIssue|8901}})
*Fix ({{en/GHIssue|8886}}): Don't try to resolve folders within tars named '.' ({{en/GHIssue|8893}})
*Fix: Placing random trees in SE crashes the game ({{en/GHIssue|8892}})
*Fix ({{en/GHIssue|8875}}): Filter string in station window breaks flow in user interface ({{en/GHIssue|8885}})
*Fix ({{en/GHIssue|8871}}): [OpenGL] Initialize all buffers after resize and clear back buffer ({{en/GHIssue|8877}})
*Fix: OpenGL performance with some AMD GPUs ({{en/GHIssue|8876}})
*Fix: Recompute road/railtype availability after disabling the engine ({{en/GHIssue|8872}})
*Fix: OSK layout not scaled for 2x or 4x GUI scale ({{en/GHIssue|8868}})


